data.description: Fantastic Lakefront Living with Direct Water View of Lake Mahopac overlooks your beautiful private beach. Enjoy sunrises and sunsets on your private balcony overlooking Lake Mahopac. This top floor unit with stunning views has 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths, hardwood floors in the living room and dining room and updated windows and sliding glass door. Primary bedroom suite with bath and walk-in-closet. Amenities include a private beach for residents, storage space, private parking and laundry located in lowest level. Conveniently located and close distance to shopping, restaurants, bike path. Breathtaking views of Lake Mahopac.
